    },
    {
      "question": "Is this scheme only for student?",
      "answer": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "question": "What is DBT?",
      "answer": "DBT stands for Direct Benefit Transfer. It is a mechanism used by governments to transfer financial assistance or subsidies directly to the bank accounts of beneficiaries."
    },
