      "answer": "The scheme aims to provide support to fishermen families facing income deprivation during natural calamities and fishing ban periods, while also conserving fishery wealth during breeding seasons."
    },
    {
      "question": "How does the scheme treat beneficiaries who are recipients of Old Age Pension (OAP)?",
