    },
    {
      "question": "Is possession of fishing boats a determining factor for eligibility?",
      "answer": "The scheme is open to all fishermen, regardless of boat possession—be it mechanized, motorized, or traditional—ensuring accessibility to a broad range of beneficiaries."
    },
