      "answer": "No, the applicant needs to visit the nearest Department of Social Welfare office to apply for the scheme."
    },
    {
      "question": "What are the documents required to apply for the scheme?",
      "answer": "Disability Certificate- Applicant must be 80% or more handicapped. Latest BPL Certificate. Copy of the Parivar Register. Aadhaar Card. Bank Account."
